<% content_for :title, "Privacy — SnagRadar" %>

<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 sm:px-8 pt-36 sm:pt-44 pb-24">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-talent-muted">Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%-d %B %Y") %></p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg mt-10 max-w-none text-talent-slate leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>This privacy policy describes how SnagRadar Ltd ("we", "us") collects and uses information when you visit our website or use our service. It is provided for transparency and is not legal advice — please consult your legal counsel for binding interpretations.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-talent-navy">What we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Information you provide when you contact us — name, work email, company, phone, message.</li>
        <li>Information your team enters into the product — site names, plot references, defect descriptions, photos, signatures.</li>
        <li>Technical information — IP address, browser type, pages visited.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-talent-navy">How we use it</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>To deliver the service you've requested (demos, pilots, support).</li>
        <li>To operate the SnagRadar product — store defects, route notifications, generate evidence.</li>
        <li>To improve the product through aggregated, de-identified analysis.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-talent-navy">Where we store it</h2>
      <p>Data is stored on EU-based infrastructure with encryption in transit and at rest. Uploaded files (photos, signatures) are kept in object storage and served via signed URLs.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-talent-navy">Your rights</h2>
      <p>You can request access, correction or deletion of your personal data at any time. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@snagradar.co.uk" class="text-talent-orange font-semibold">privacy@snagradar.co.uk</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-talent-navy">Contact</h2>
      <p>SnagRadar Ltd, London, United Kingdom. Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@snagradar.co.uk" class="text-talent-orange font-semibold">privacy@snagradar.co.uk</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
